Occupation: Chef

Name: John Doe
Age: 32
Gender: Male
Occupation: Construction worker
Ethnicity: African American
Past Medical History: Diagnosed with HIV/AIDS 5 years ago. Currently taking antiretroviral therapy (ART) and has a history of sexually transmitted infections (STIs). Also has a history of substance abuse, including injection drug use. Has had multiple hospitalizations for HIV-related complications, including pneumonia and Kaposi's sarcoma. Is currently being managed by an infectious disease specialist and a mental health professional.

Occupation: Unemployed
